  • public class IfxColumnInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Note: We may put this class in ResultSetMetaData class as nested class in the future. That is the only place use this class. This is a class object contains all information about a column. It is mainly for ResultSetMetaData class. All instant variables are declared as public. It is easy access from ResultSetMetaData class.
